<% content_for :title, "Privacy Policy | Pasabaya.app " %>

<div class="bg-white min-h-screen py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <a href="/" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500 font-medium flex items-center mb-8">
      <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"></path>
      </svg>
      Back to home
    </a>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-indigo prose-lg text-gray-500 space-y-6">
      <p class="text-sm italic">Last Updated: March 27, 2026</p>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>At <strong>Pasabaya.app</strong>, we take your privacy seriously. This policy explains how we handle your
          personal data in
          compliance with the <strong>Philippine Data Privacy Act of 2012 (RA 10173)</strong>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">2. Data We Collect</h2>
        <p>We only collect information that you voluntarily provide to us when you sign up for our waitlist:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>Full Name</li>
          <li>Email Address</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">3. Purpose of Processing</h2>
        <p>Your data is collected solely to notify you about the project launch and related updates. We do not sell your
          data to third parties.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">4. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We use industry-standard security measures (SSL/TLS encryption) to protect your data. Your information is
          stored on secure servers managed via AWS.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">5. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Under the DPA of 2012, you have the right to access, correct, or request the deletion of your personal data
          at any time. To exercise these rights, please contact us at
          <strong>privacy@pasabaya.app</strong>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
